### 4. Protect matched blocks in DRC Critic

#### [MODIFY] [nodes.py](file:///c:/Users/DELL%20G3/Desktop/GP/Automation/AI-Automation-New/ai_agent/ai_chat_bot/nodes.py) — `node_drc_critic`

Before applying any DRC fix (prescriptive or LLM):
- Check if the target device has `_matched_block` tag.
- If yes → skip individual coordinate adjustment. Instead, move the **entire block as rigid body** (same delta to all members).

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is the critical "block locking" mechanism. Without it, the DRC critic will break matching every time.

---

