#### [MODIFY] [nodes.py](file:///c:/Users/DELL%20G3/Desktop/GP/Automation/AI-Automation-New/ai_agent/ai_chat_bot/nodes.py) — `node_sa_optimizer` + sa_optimizer.py

Matched block member IDs should be added to `chain_member_ids` so SA never swaps them.

